[[Image:Triton_moon_mosaic_Voyager_2_(large).jpg|thumb]]
'''[[海卫一|海卫一]]的大氣層'''延伸至距離地表800[[公里|公里]]的地區<ref name="Voyager">{{cite web | url = http://voyager.jpl.nasa.gov/science/neptune_triton.html | title = Triton | work = Voyager | accessdate = 2007-12-31 | archive-date = 2011-10-05 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/62D2qBMev?url=http://voyager.jpl.nasa.gov/science/neptune_triton.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，主要由[[氮氣|氮氣]]所構成，成份類似[[土衛六|土衛六]][[大氣層|大氣層]]與[[地球大氣層|地球大氣層]]<ref name="Solar System">{{cite web|url=http://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/profile.cfm?Object=Nep_Triton |title=Neptune: Moons: Triton |work=Solar System Exploration |accessdate=2007-12-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110095537/http://solarsystem.nasa.gov/planets/profile.cfm?Object=Nep_Triton |archivedate=2008-01-10 }}</ref>。海卫一大氣層的表面[[氣壓|氣壓]]只有14微[[巴|巴]]，為地球的1/70,000<ref name="Voyager"/>。[[天文學家|天文學家]]原本認為海卫一擁有濃厚的大氣層，但是[[航海家二號|航海家二號]]在1989年首次近距離探測海卫一的大氣層後推翻這種看法。近年來的天文觀測則顯示海卫一的大氣層含量正在逐漸增加當中<ref name="MIT Triton"/>。

==組成成份==
[[Image:Triton's_atmosphere.jpg|thumb]]

[[氮氣|氮氣]]是海卫一大氣層中最主要的成分，目前也發現有[[甲烷|甲烷]]存在<ref name="The Grand Tour">{{cite book |title=The Grand Tour: A Traveler's Guide to the Solar System|last= Miller|first= Ron|authorlink= Ron Miller (artist and author)|coauthors=William K. Hartmann|pages= 172–173|publisher= Workman Publishing|location= Thailand|edition= 3rd|isbn= 0-7611-3547-2|date=May 2005}}</ref>。其他[[行星|行星]]及[[衛星|衛星]]上也存在成份類似的大氣層，例如[[地球|地球]]及土衛六<ref name="Solar System"/>。

==結構==
海卫一大氣層的結構相當完整並遍佈整個衛星.<ref name="Voyager"/>。海卫一大氣層延伸至距離地表800[[公里|公里]]的地區，表面的[[氣壓|氣壓]]只有14微[[巴|巴]]，大約是地球大氣層的1/70,000。海卫一的表面溫度至少高於[[攝氏|攝氏]]−237.6度（35.6[[熱力學溫標|K]]），因為天文學家發現表面的氮冰處於比較溫暖的環境下才會出現的六角形結晶狀<ref name="Duxburyetal1993">{{cite journal
 | title = The Phase Composition of Triton's Polar Caps
 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Sci...261..748D
 | author = N S Duxbury, R H Brown
 | journal = Science
 | issn = 0036-8075
 | volume = 261
 | issue = 5122
 | pages = 748–751
 | date = August 1993
 | accessdate = 2008-01-24
 | doi = 10.1126/science.261.5122.748
 | archive-date = 2016-01-10
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110101516/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Sci...261..748D
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。而溫度上限則會低於40K，這是根據海卫一大氣層的氮氣處於壓力平衡之下所推算的結果<ref>{{cite journal
 | title = Spectroscopic Determination of the Phase Composition and Temperature of Nitrogen Ice on Triton
 | author = Kimberly Tryka, Robert Brown, V. Anicich et al.
 | journal = Science
 | issn = 0036-8075
 | volume = 261
 | issue = 5122
 | pages = 751–754
 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Sci...261..751T
 | date = August 1993
 | accessdate = 2008-01-24
 | doi = 10.1126/science.261.5122.751
 | archive-date = 2016-01-10
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110101519/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Sci...261..751T
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。海卫一表面的擾動則會產生高達8[[公里|公里]]的[[對流層|對流層]]<ref name=nature/>，但是海卫一大氣層並沒有[[平流層|平流層]]<ref name="book">{{cite book|last= McKinnon|first= William B.|coauthors= Randolph L. Kirk |title=  Encyclopedia of the Solar System|origyear= 2007|edition= 2nd.|publisher= Academic Press|isbn= 0120885891|pages= 483–502|chapter= Triton|chapterurl= |quote=|year= 2007 }}</ref>。海卫一大氣層的溫度隨高度上升而遞減，[[對流頂層|對流頂層]]的溫度約為36K<ref name=Smith1989/>。海拔更高的地區則依序分成[[熱成層|熱成層]]、[[電離層|電離層]]及[[逸散層|逸散層]]<ref name="Model">{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/0273-1177(92)90427-Y| title = A model of Triton's atmosphere and ionosphere | author =  Lellouch, E.; Blanc, M.; Oukbir J.; and Longaretti, P.-Y.| journal = Advances in Space Research| volume = 12| year = 1992| pages = pp. 113–121}}</ref>。[[逸散層|逸散層]]的溫度約為75K。

==天氣==

氮粒子在海卫一表面幾公里高的地方形成[[雲|雲]]<ref name="Voyager"/>，而天文學家也發現霧的存在<ref name="Nine Planets">{{cite web|url=http://www.nineplanets.org/triton.html|title=Triton|work=nineplanets.org|accessdate=2007-12-31|archive-date=2007-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071217223336/http://www.nineplanets.org/triton.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些霧被認為主要是由[[烴|烴]]及[[腈|腈]]（由受到陽光照射的甲烷所產生的<ref name=book/>）所組成的。海卫一大氣層也擁有固體氮所構成的雲系，並位在距離地表1至3公里高的位置。天文學家也普遍在海拔8公里的地方發現[[風|風]]的存在，這是由極地及[[赤道|赤道]]地區的溫差所產生的<ref name="Wind direction"/>。這些風也包含著大小超過1[[微米|微米]]的遊離物質<ref name=nature>{{cite journal
 | title = Voyager 2 at Neptune: Imaging Science Results
 | author = B A Smith, L A Soderblom et al.
 | journal = Science
 | issn = 0036-8075
 | volume = 246
 | pages = 1422–1449
 | date = December 15, 1989
 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1989Sci...246.1422S
 | accessdate = 2008-01-15
 | doi = 10.1126/science.246.4936.1422
 | archive-date = 2016-01-10
 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160110101525/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1989Sci...246.1422S
 | dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。海卫一大氣層中間也受到超音速的風所影響，包括海卫一的[[光度曲線|光度曲線]]<ref name="Distorted">{{cite journal |last=Elliot |first=J. L. |coauthors=J. A. Stansberry, C. B. Olkin, M. A. Agner, M. E. Davies |title=Triton's Distorted Atmosphere |journal=Science |volume=278 |pages=pp. 436–439 |id=10.1126 |url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/278/5337/436 |accessdate=2007-12-31 |doi=10.1126/science.278.5337.436 |date=October 1997 |archive-date=2001-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20010307174745/http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/278/5337/436 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。低海拔的風則從南半球往北半球吹拂<ref name="Wind direction">{{cite journal|last= Ingersoll|first= Andrew P.|title= Dynamics of Triton's atmosphere|journal= Nature|volume= 344|pages= pp. 315–317|id= 10.1038/344315a|url= http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v344/n6264/abs/344315a0.html|accessdate= 2008-04-12|doi= 10.1038/344315a0|date= March 1990|archive-date= 2008-07-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080726030023/http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v344/n6264/abs/344315a0.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。航海家二號曾在極區觀測到[[反氣旋|反氣旋]]形成，這是因為霜昇華所造成的。這個氣旋的風速則約為秒速5 <sup>-1</sup>.<ref name="Wind direction"/>。

==觀測及探測活動==
===航海家二號之前===
在航海家二號近距離探測海卫一之前，天文學家認為它由氮及甲烷構成的大氣層密度約為地球大氣層的30%。目前已經知道這個估計值過於偏高，就像天文學家原本對於[[火星大氣層|火星大氣層]]的密度估計也過高一樣<ref name="Icarus">{{cite journal| doi= 10.1016/0019-1035(92)90031-2|title=A massive early atmosphere on Triton|author=Lunine, J. I.; and Nolan, Michael C.|journal= Icarus|volume= 100|year= 1992|pages= pp. 221–234}}</ref>。

===航海家二號通過===
航海家二號在1989年以最近距離來通過[[海王星|海王星]]5小時之後接近海卫一<ref name="New York Times">{{cite web|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DE7DC113DF931A1575BC0A96F948260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all|title=Profile of Neptune's Main Moon: Small, Bright, Cold, and It's Pink|work=The New York Times|last=Wilford|first=John|accessdate=2007-12-31|archive-date=2008-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080110105900/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=950DE7DC113DF931A1575BC0A96F948260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>，
當時航海家二號也對海卫一大氣層進行探測<ref name="Triton Background">{{Cite web|url=http://www.boulder.swri.edu/TritonWatch/background.html|title=Triton: Background and Science|work=PLANETARY SCIENCE DIRECTORATE Boulder Office|accessdate=2007-12-31|archive-date=2008-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080119204707/http://www.boulder.swri.edu/TritonWatch/background.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並且在大氣層中發現氮及甲烷的存在<ref name="The Grand Tour"/>。

===後續的觀測===
在1990年代，天文學家從地球上藉由海卫一的[[掩星|掩星]]現象來觀測它的[[周邊昏暗|周邊昏暗]]情形。這些觀測結果顯示海卫一大氣層的密度比航海家二號探測的結果還要高<ref name="Hubblesite">{{cite web | url = http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/newsdesk/archive/releases/1998/23/text/ | title = Hubble Space Telescope Helps Find Evidence that Neptune's Largest Moon Is Warming Up | work = Hubblesite | author = Savage, D.; Weaver, D.; and Halber, D | accessdate = 2007-12-31 | archive-date = 2011-10-05 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/62D2r1C3B?url=http://hubblesite.org/newscenter/newsdesk/archive/releases/1998/23/text/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> ，而其他的觀測結果則顯示海卫一大氣層的溫度從1989年至1998年間上升5%<ref name="MIT Triton">{{cite web | title=MIT researcher finds evidence of global warming on Neptune's largest moon | url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1998/triton.html | date=1998-06-24 | publisher=[[Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology|Massachusetts Institute of Technology]] | accessdate=2007-12-31 | archive-date=2011-10-05 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/62D2r8yOL?url=http://web.mit.edu/newsoffice/1998/triton.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。這篇報告的作者[[詹姆斯·勒德洛·埃利奧特|詹姆斯·勒德洛·埃利奧特]]則說<ref name="MIT Triton"/>：

{{cquote|至少從1989年開始，海卫一正在經歷一段全球暖化。從百分比來看，它增加的幅度非常巨大。}}

這些觀測顯示海卫一經歷一段不尋常的溫暖夏季，僅僅在幾百年間才會發生一次。關於暖化的解釋包括地表模型的改變、冰反射率的改變讓更多熱量可以被留在大氣層中<ref name="Scienceagogo.com">{{cite web | title=Global Warming Detected on Triton | url=http://www.scienceagogo.com/news/19980526052143data_trunc_sys.shtml | date=1998-05-28 | publisher=Scienceagogo.com | accessdate=2007-12-31 | archive-date=2007-12-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214235332/http://www.scienceagogo.com/news/19980526052143data_trunc_sys.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他的理論則認為溫度的變化是暗色物質沉澱所造成的，這些紅色的物質是海卫一的地質活動所造成的。因為海卫一的[[球面反照率|球面反照率]]是[[太陽系|太陽系]]所有天體當中最高的，所以細微的反射率改變都會造成影響<ref name="Nature">{{cite journal|title=Does global warming make Triton blush? |url=http://www.bio.indiana.edu/~palmerlab/Journals/170.pdf |last=Buratti |first=Bonnie J. |coauthors=Michael D. Hicks, Ray L. Newburn Jr |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]] |volume=397 |issue=6716 |date=1999-01-21 |pages=219 |doi=10.1038/16615 |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |accessdate=2007-12-31 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070611233151/http://www.bio.indiana.edu/~palmerlab/Journals/170.pdf |archivedate=2007-06-11 }}</ref>。

===觀測海卫一===
觀測海卫一計畫集合天文學家來監測海卫一的溫度變化，這項觀測計畫的資金則是由[[NASA|NASA]]所提供的<ref name="Triton Watch">{{cite web|url=http://www.boulder.swri.edu/TritonWatch/about.html|title=About the Triton Watch Project|work=PLANETARY SCIENCE DIRECTORATE Boulder Office|accessdate=2007-12-31|archive-date=2008-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080119204656/http://www.boulder.swri.edu/TritonWatch/about.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

